<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      /* Add your custom styles here */
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .logo {
        max-width: 150px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .message {
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
      .message h2 {
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .message p {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
        color: #999;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <img
          class="logo"
          src="https://w7.pngwing.com/pngs/945/519/png-transparent-health-administration-hospital-information-system-management-software-development-altarama-information-systems-medicine-ophthalmology-hospital-thumbnail.png"
          alt="Logo"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="message">
        <h2>Thank you for contacting us!</h2>
        <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>
        <p>
          We appreciate your interest in our services. Our team has received
          your message and will get back to you shortly.
        </p>
        <p>Here are the details of your inquiry:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Name:</strong> <%= name %></li>
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></li>
          <li><strong>Message:</strong> <%= content %></li>
        </ul>
        <p>If you have any further questions, feel free to reach out to us.</p>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>The Example Company Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Â©MediSys Company. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
